Title: Sending metrics to Graphite/InfluxDB can now be disabled for services
Level: 2
Edition: cee
Component: cmc
Compatible: compat
Version: 1.4.0i1
Date: 1460552393
Class: feature

When sending metrics to Graphite/InfluxDB is enabled it was not possible to
disable the export for specific services. We have now added the ruleset
<i>Enable/disable sending Graphite/InfluxDB metrics</i> to configure this
for services individually. By default all metrics are sent as before.
